most important political force in Kazakhstan, although it is still
young, and the CPC is willing to deepen mutual understanding with
"Otan" and strive to promote bilateral friendship through joint
efforts.
</P>
<P>
S.A. Tereshchenko, president of "Otan" and head of the
delegation, said Kazakhstan has great interest in China's
experience in reform and opening up, expects to expand bilateral
cooperation, and welcomes more Chinese enterprises to invest in
his country.  
