<HEADLINE> Diplomatic News Highlights </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 27 (Xinhua) -- Following is the highlights of the
diplomatic news released by Xinhua here today:
</P>
<P>
Signed Article Condemns U.S. Hegemony
</P>
<P>
The so-called "global democratization" theory is just a
camouflage for the United States to engage in hegemony, said a
senior researcher in a signed article today.
</P>
<P>
Wang Jincun, of the Chinese Academy of Social Sciences, wrote
in the article that the so-called "global democratization" theory
is just part of the numerous power politics theories put forward
by the United States.
</P>
<P>
The article has about 3,000 Chinese characters.
</P>
<P>
CPPCC National Committee Chairman Returns to Beijing
</P>
<P>
