Fuzhou police took notice of the illegal immigration plan some two
weeks ago, as several ROK citizens paid frequent visits to the
city and plotted with some local snakeheads.
</P>
<P>
An investigation led police to the people who tried to use an
ROK boat to smuggle the Chines citizens, and after the boat
arrived at Mawei Port in Fuzhou on May 25 it was placed under
close police surveillance. 
