<HEADLINE> 46th WFA Congress Opens in Seoul </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SEOUL, May 27 (Xinhua) -- The 46th congress of the World
Federation of Advertisers (WFA) starts here in Seoul with
participation of more than 500 deputies from 40 countries.
</P>
<P>
The two-day congress, under the theme "Challenges in the New
Millennium," will discuss the challenges and opportunities amid
fast progressing information and media technology on the threshold
of the new millennium.
</P>
<P>
WFA World Congress is the only world scale advertisers
conference,which has been held every two years in turn among WFA
member countries.
</P>
<P>
WFA is a Brussels-based international organization, whose
members include 40 countries' advertisers associations and 24
multinational corporations.
</P>
<P>
It promotes the positive roles of advertising for the welfare
of people as well as the freedom of commercial expression and
fights against irrational regulations on advertising activities.
