<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 27 (Xinhua) -- Direct or indirect incorporation of
Taiwan in the Japanese-U.S. defense cooperation is a violation of
China's sovereignty and an interference in the country's internal
affairs, Foreign Ministry spokesman Zhu Bangzao said here today at
a press conference.
</P>
<P>
