<HEADLINE> Sri Lanka to Host Investment Conference </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, May 27 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lanka will host a two-day
investor conference in a bid to raise the profile of the country
among foreign and local fund managers, officials said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
